{"search_data": "PunjabHow to Apply Online for New Punjab Ration Card or Download Application Form PDF & Details Complete procedure on how to apply online for Punjab ration card or the new smart ration card in Punjab in 2020 at punjab.gov.in. Also see the list of documents required and helpline details for any ration card related query.Ration Card is an essential document for the APL / BPL people to take benefits of most Punjab govt. schemes. It is important to note that ration card holders only can purchase Ration at subsidized rates from Ration Shops located nearby.Table of Contents  How to Apply for Punjab Smart Ration CardPunjab Ration Card Online Application InstructionsPunjab Ration Card Offline Application InstructionsRation Card Search / Status / Beneficiary DetailsNew Punjab Ration Card \u2013 Update Details FormPunjab Ration Card Documents List to Apply OnlinePunjab Ration Card HelplineHow to Apply for Punjab Smart Ration CardPunjab ration card applications can be made through both online and offline modes as given below.Punjab Ration Card Online Application InstructionsOn the State Portal of Punjab, click on Citizen Login link.If you are a new user, click on \u201cNew User\u201d link, else login with your Username and Password.After logging in for the first time, user will be asked to update their profile. Please update it.Click on \u201cFresh Application\u201d link in the left menu.On the next screen, all Department wise services are listed. Choose the service you want to apply for and click the \u201cApply\u201d link next to the service.On the Fresh Application screen, go to Alternative 2 (Online Form application) section and click on \u201cClick here to fill the application form online\u201d link.Fill the form and click \u201cSubmit\u201d.Click \u201cView Saved Application\u201d link, select the application and click \u201cUpload Supporting Documents\u201d button.Upload the supporting documents and your application is complete.Punjab Ration Card Offline Application InstructionsOn the State Portal of Punjab, click on Citizen Login link.If you are a new user, click on \u201cNew User\u201d link, else login with your Username and Password.After logging in for the first time, user will be asked to update their profile. Please update it.Click on \u201cFresh Application\u201d link in the left menu.On the next screen, all Department wise services are listed. Choose the service you want to apply for and click the \u201cApply\u201d link next to the service.On the Fresh Application screen, go to Alternative 1(Offline Form application) section and click on Form Name to download the e-Form.Fill the e-Form in offline mode (Internet connection is not required to fill e-Form).Login to the application and on the Fresh Application screen, go to Alternative 1 (Offline Form application) section and click on \u201cClick here to upload the filled form\u201d link.Browse to the filled e-Form and click on \u201cAdd\u201d button.Visit the official portal of Punjab at punjab.gov.in.Ration Card Search / Status / Beneficiary DetailsAll the applications who have applied for the new smart ration card or the beneficiaries who already own Punjab Ration card can check ration card details or the status and the beneficiary details by entering their ration card number, Aadhar number or SRC number.Ration Card Search by RC No. \u2013 Click Here Punjab Ration Card Beneficiary Details \u2013 Click Here Ration Card Search (Aadhar Card) \u2013 Click HereNew Punjab Ration Card \u2013 Update Details FormHere we are providing you the direct link to download Punjab Ration Card Form PDF for updating the details through online mode which is mentioned belowChange / Add Member Details FormThe new Punjab Ration Card form PDF will appear as shown below:Ration Card Form PDF Download PunjabPunjab Ration Card Documents List to Apply OnlineHere is the complete list of required documents (\u0a5b\u0a30\u0a42\u0a30\u0a40 \u0a26\u0a38\u0a24\u0a3e\u0a35\u0a47\u0a1c\u0a3e\u0